data.description: PRICE REDUCED, SELLERS SUPER MOTIVATED, YOU DON'T WANT TO MISS THIS INCREDIBLE PREMIUM CORNER LOT HOME WITH SOLAR PANELS SYSTEM INCLUDED AND CONSERVATION VIEW, Price reduced! ¡¡BEING A GREAT SEXY DEAL!!, This beautiful ENERGY STAR CERTIFIED single-story home in Rivercrest at Narcoossee. Home sits on a PREMIUM corner lot and features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and 2 car garage. model home with a functional floor plan that features volume ceilings, designer tile flooring throughout the Great room, kitchen and bathrooms. This open kitchen with big countertops, eat-at island, and 36-in. upper wood cabinets with all stainless-steel appliances included. This home really does have it all. The only thing missing is you! The community offers a resort-style pool, clubhouse, playground and dog park. Fantastic location as you will have easy commute to Lake Nona Medical City, Nemours Hospital and VA hospital. Zoned for top rated Narcoossee Elementary, Middle Schools and Harmony High.
